Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.28,0:00:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纷争从一个小小的契机开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并发展成了巨大的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种各样的人 形形色色的思绪相互冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而酿成了巨大的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是非常可悲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争给我带来巨大的悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于人类使用自己所无法驾驭的巨大力量之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在反省的同时 我也感到深深的后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承前代皇帝雷伊雷嘉利亚·巴斯·雷巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登基为巴斯帝国的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并下嫁给轨道骑士37家族之一的库鲁迪欧伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们巴斯帝国皇室希望与地球讲和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以巴斯帝国女王之名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令听到广播的全部轨道骑士立刻停战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主殿下不是要和托罗亚特伯爵建立新王朝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么对联合军的总攻击要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 现在先别轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静观事态发展 看看风会吹向哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底托罗亚特伯爵就是个下贱的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不配攀上王室贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.09,0:01:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈库莱特爵士 我们返航！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:44.04,title,NTP,0,0,0,,“那天看到的流星”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还在战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下刚宣布停战了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月面基地那边的军队可是干劲满满的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 不要放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的那位亚瑟拉姆公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆女王是我所认识的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被界冢少尉料中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么停战的命令也是货真价实的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的敌人好像并不打算结束战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部那边有什么指示吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有下达任何指示 继续执行作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月面基地和扬陆城都没有表现出任何停战的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆女王的所在位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的通信是从马兹卢卡伯爵的扬陆城发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她舍弃月球了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说他们内部分裂了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托罗亚特伯爵 亚瑟拉姆陛下的懿旨要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懿旨？你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到…会出这么一手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷姆蕾娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正重要的东西是王族的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拥有Aldnoah的启动权
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以实现你的愿望 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪里都不会去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的归宿只有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的深情厚意 雷姆蕾娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说太轻佻了吧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那些光芒中飞驰的同时也看到了很多的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了一切 不管是好的还是坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所能看到的只是片刻之后的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本以为看穿了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多事情的展开也正如我所看到的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却没有看到什么才是真正重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进行补给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托罗亚特伯爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主殿下为什么会…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我接通司令室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全军 也包括出击中的Stygis队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员10分以内撤离月面基地！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和扬陆城一起向联合军投降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃这个月面基地！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷姆蕾娜公主 对于至今为止的无礼行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深感抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿您健康长寿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈库莱特 请护送雷姆蕾娜公主到航天机上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 斯雷因！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下 请往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不走！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因！斯雷因！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检测到月面基地那边出现了许多新的机影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是援军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们正离开战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月面基地…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷落了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自爆了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈库莱特大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航天机的护卫就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈库莱特大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈库莱特 你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了 快去投降！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈库莱特！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis队 不要擅自行动！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌增援部队接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10点钟方向 仰角-10！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎战准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！我们已经没有胜算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别白白浪费生命！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已做好了觉悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅我的任性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去投降吧 哈库莱特！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法听从这个命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个动作是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错呢 哈库莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就这样结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事情没有做完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来接你了 斯雷因·托罗亚特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来作个了断吧 界冢伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你如何预测攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要逃不掉的话就毫无意义！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃不了的人是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:53.32,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Unknown soldier lying on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.28,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Explosions forever
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:58.95,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Now you take me away from danger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开接触线路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.99,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}We had always covered up your face
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解密协议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得问也没有意义 但还是问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:06.16,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Out there who will watch your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投降吧 斯雷因·托罗亚特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:09.04,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Because I don't know if I can stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是为了说这种无聊的话来找我的吗 界冢伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.13,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Game over
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:14.34,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Now we hate our brothers
