Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.88,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I will be there for you and please wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.26,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh you must believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.80,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Better you believe your mind
